article.description: Bryce Aiken had 19 points as Harvard beat Penn 66-58 in the Ivy League tournament semifinals on Saturday.
article.headline: Aiken scores 19, Harvard tops Penn 66-58 in Ivy League
article.linkText: Aiken scores 19, Harvard tops Penn 66-58 in Ivy League
article.story: NEW HAVEN, Conn. -- Bryce Aiken had 19 points as Harvard beat Penn 66-58 in the Ivy League tournament semifinals on Saturday. Noah Kirkwood had 12 points for Harvard (18-10). Kale Catchings added nine rebounds. AJ Brodeur had 25 points and 10 rebounds for the Quakers (19-12).
